'''Dáin''' can refer to two [[Dwarves]]:

* [[Dáin I]] ({{TA|2440}} -  {{TA|2589|n}}), [[Kings of Durin's Folk|King]] of [[Durin's Folk]] who was killed by a [[cold-drake]].
* [[Dáin Ironfoot|Dáin II ''Ironfoot'']] ({{TA|2767}} - {{TA|3019|n}}), [[Lord of the Iron Hills]] who became King of Durin's Folk following the death of [[Thorin|Thorin II ''Oakenshield'']].
